data.title: Runtime error on Ubuntu 22.04 - Could not load the Qt platform plugin "xcb" · Issue #5974 · biolab/orange3
data.meta_description: When I execute the command python3 -m Orange.canvas i get the following error: Warning: Ignoring XDG_SESSION_TYPE=wayland on Gnome. Use QT_QPA_PLATFORM=wayland to run on Wayland anyway. qt.qpa.plugin: Could not load the Qt platform plugi...
